original_title: The Daryl Hall & John Oates Video Collection: 7 Big Ones
overview: Video collection of some of their biggest hits.  "Say It Isn't So", "Family Man", "Maneater", "Private Eyes", "Adult Education", "I Can't Go For That (No Can Do)" and "One On One".
title: The Daryl Hall & John Oates Video Collection: 7 Big Ones
